descriptions.value: The R8 Revolver delivers a highly accurate and powerful round at the expense of a lengthy trigger-pull. Firing rapidly by fanning the hammer may be the best option when point-blank stopping power is required. It has been custom painted with a purple barrel and a number 8 on the grip. Inspired by the events of December 8th, 2015
